window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>This Is Not a Game</i> is the extraordinary untold story of the internet’s first conspiracy theory, the legend of Ong’s Hat.</p> <p>Marc Fennell will dive deep into a previously unexplored world of tech hippies, eccentric web subcultures and simmering paranoia, uncovering how this tongue-in-cheek artistic experiment backfired on its creator and went on to influence much of what’s wrong with the internet today.</p> <p>Hosted and co-produced by Marc Fennell</p> <p>A BBC Studios production for Audible</p>"; 
